  "notes": "Before 2018, BMW Group’s development fleet relied on manual data transfer and on-premises data processing, significantly slowing vehicle development and prototype cycles.\n\nThe company created a mobile data recorder (MDR) solution, placing an IoT device in each development car to transmit data over a cellular connection to an Azure cloud platform, where Azure AI and data solutions facilitate efficient data analysis.\n\nThe MDR system and copilot fueled by Azure significantly enhances data accessibility, speeds prototypes and troubleshooting, and elevates development quality.\n\nhttps://www.microsoft.com/en/customers/story/19769-bmw-ag-azure-app-service"
}